replies.body:
@Meddler :

I had a Idea, not sure if anyone tought about it. You can only buy the Cinderhulk when you have Smite as a Summoner Spell right?.
So why dont limit the Smite Spells per Team to 1?. So only one Summoner per Team can pick Smite. Sure there is the Chance that the Toplane picks it and refuse to give it to the Jungel, but then you can Report the Top-Lane and the "Troll" in that Case gets Punished right?.

I only saw that you plan to move the Damage and all that Stuff and i tought "why not simply limit the Smites per Team?". That would, in my Opinion, solve the Problem and still leaves the Jungle Tanks in a Good Spot so they are still usefull

@Ahri Desu: Not broken, usefull. If they get nerfed again there is again no reason to choose a Tanky Jungel like Seju or something over VI or Xin.
